## 5. Key Security Indicator (KSI) Definitions

- **KSI-IAM (Identity):** Real-time authentication logs from **Microsoft Entra ID**.
- **KSI-PIY (Inventory):** Deterministic asset discovery via **Infoblox** APIs.
- **KSI-MLA (Monitoring):** Network health and path data from **Cisco/Microsoft INR**.
- **KSI-SVC (Crypto):** mTLS certificate enforcement at the Overlay layer.
- **KSI-CMT (Change):** GitHub YAML baseline drift detection.
- **KSI-CNA (Network):** Packet-level identity metadata from SD-WAN telemetry.
- **KSI-CED (Privacy):** Data minimization enforcement at Identity and Overlay layers.

